  </div>
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-10/xiaobian2.jpg?bM9ghAAVi2TSxf51.84NKUNIMiy6Lrd2&itok=FHuYREmb" alt data-caption="三名航天员今天一同打开睡眠区，配合十分默契。（视频截图）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-10/xiaobian2.jpg?bM9ghAAVi2TSxf51.84NKUNIMiy6Lrd2&itok=FHuYREmb" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
